sentences.sentence: "It took longer than we wanted," Clemens said after notching his first victory since June 9.
sentences.translation: “用的时间比我们希望的要长，”克莱门斯在6月9日以来赢得他的第一次胜利后说。

sentences.sentence: Export growth also slowed but by a smaller margin, notching a 21.1% increase.
sentences.translation: 出口增幅也出现下降，但降幅较小，当月增长了21.1%。

sentences.sentence: This means that the system only improves, always notching forward, never backsliding.
sentences.translation: 这意味着系统只能够被改进，总是向前的，从不会倒退。
